      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BUBBLE COASTER (8) had second look this course and distance latest and improved on her time, finishing a 2 length third in 20.37. Rates a top chance if runs up to latest. CASH CARRIAGE (7) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (20.58) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Can improve sharply here. MICK SAID SO (5) shows ability but remains a maiden after seven starts. Was below best last time when missed the frame finishing fourth (20.87) at this track. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in two starts. Cannot be underestimated. GULF STREAM (2) has to be respected despite coming off a seven weeks break.",
